<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8"/>
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1"/>
<title>Score de Engajamento de E-mail</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Chivo:wght@400;500;700;900&family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet"/>
<style>
  *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
  :root {
    --orange: #FF6D01; --orange-dim: #CC5700;
    --bg: #0D0D0D; --bg2: #141414; --bg3: #1C1C1C; --bg4: #242424;
    --border: rgba(255,255,255,0.08); --border-orange: rgba(255,109,1,0.35);
    --text: #F5F0E8; --text-muted: rgba(245,240,232,0.5); --text-dim: rgba(245,240,232,0.25);
    --font-head: 'Chivo', sans-serif; --font-body: 'Inter', sans-serif;
  }
  html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
  body { background: var(--bg); color: var(--text); font-family: var(--font-body); min-height: 100vh; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; }
  
  .hero {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 24px 24px 32px;
    position: relative;
  }
  .hero h1 {
    font-family: var(--font-head);
    font-size: clamp(24px, 4vw, 40px);
    font-weight: 900;
    line-height: 1.1;
    letter-spacing: -.02em;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
    display: inline-block;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }
  .hero h1 em { font-style: normal; color: var(--orange); }
  .hero p { font-size: 14px; color: var(--text-muted); max-width: 420px; margin: 0 auto; line-height: 1.4; }

  .wrap { max-width: 860px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 20px 64px; }
  
  .card { background: var(--bg2); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 4px; padding: 20px; margin-bottom: 20px; }
  
  .final-card { background: var(--bg2); border: 1px solid var(--border-orange); border-radius: 4px; padding: 32px 24px 28px; text-align: center; position: relative; overflow: hidden; }
  .final-score { font-family: var(--font-head); font-size: 72px; font-weight: 900; line-height: 1; color: var(--text); letter-spacing: -.04em; margin-bottom: 14px; }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="hero">
  <h1>Score de <em>Engajamento</em></h1>
  <p>Ajuste os valores e veja o score calculado em tempo real</p>
</div>

<div class="wrap">
  <div class="card">
    <h2>Médias de referência</h2>
    <p>Benchmark histórico</p>
  </div>

  <div class="card">
    <h2>Valores da campanha</h2>
    <p>Resultados desta campanha</p>
  </div>

  <div class="final-card">
    <div class="final-score">82,4</div>
    <p class="final-interp">Excelente</p>
  </div>
</div>

</body>
</html>
